{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cd731fed15","title":"右派言论——歪曲整风运动","origin":"《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b9c753e74e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"cd731fed15"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"67b01672c7","name":"湖北医学院"},{"id":"aa5e9a3445","name":"袁肇金"},{"id":"e2f4c5a94d","name":"李雨亭"},{"id":"e918d50ffc","name":"杨则俊"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"188e7f1df9","type":"title","text":"右派言论——歪曲整风运动","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd731fed15"},{"id":"7dd19981ee","type":"authors","text":"湖北医学院杨则俊袁肇金李雨亭","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd731fed15"},{"id":"a971877b6e","type":"paragraph","text":"“党的干部政策是宗派主义的根源。对干部的使用培养连封建社会都不如，因为科举制度还能选择出真才实学。”（湖北医学院  杨则俊）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd731fed15"},{"id":"52903f4c74","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们这一回把党员搞下来几个，……科以下群众我们不管，我们的目标是对准党及党员。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd731fed15"},{"id":"77f8be9fc9","type":"paragraph","text":"“过去土改、三反，肃反都是狂暴雨地搞为什么偏偏这一次提倡和风细雨呢？这样作是阻碍‘鸣’‘放’，只会使邪气上升。”（湖北医学院  袁肇金）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd731fed15"},{"id":"80666fdf57","type":"paragraph","text":"“过去是暴风暴雨，这次为什么这样‘压’？我们学校的党很坏，运动搞别人很起劲，搞自己就不干。”（湖北医学院  李雨亭）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd731fed15"}],"page":{"id":"a90adccaed","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd731fed15","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}